The evidence with the title 'Trump's approval rating drops to new low of 36% ' says Mar 27, 2017  ... Trump 's current 36% is two percentage points below Barack Obama's low point of 38 % , recorded in 2011 and 2014. ... John F. Kennedy 's lowest approval rating was 56 % ; Dwight Eisenhower 's was48%. ... His approval rating dropped to 37 % in june 1993 but recovered to 56 % by september of that year. 
